text: Carlos Carrasco Rodríguez (born 14 February 1993) is a Spanish footballer who plays as a winger for Tercera División side Intercity. ==Career== Carrasco started his senior career with Segunda División B side Orihuela before joining Eerste Divisie side Dordrecht in July 2013. After making three league appearances for Dordrecht, Carrasco returned to Spain to have spells with Jove Español, Arroyo, Orihuela and Almoradí. In February 2017, he joined 1. deild karla side Leiknir, making six league appearances for the side in the 2017 season. After Leiknir were relegated, he remained with the side for the 2018 season in 2. deild karla, playing seven more times in the league. On 21 March 2019, Carrasco joined Segunda Regional de la Comunidad Valenciana side Alicante City. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Footballers from Alicante (city) Category:Spanish footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Segunda División B players Category:Tercera División players Category:1. deild karla players Category:2. deild karla players Category:Orihuela CF players Category:FC Dordrecht players Category:Spanish expatriate footballers Category:Spanish expatriate sportspeople in Iceland Category:Spanish expatriate sportspeople in the Netherlands
